  <brief_title>Efficacy of TAK-438 Compared to AG-1749 (Lansoprazole) in the Maintenance Treatment of Healed Erosive Esophagitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Randomized, Double-Blind, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Efficacy and Safety of TAK-438 (10 mg or 20 mg Once-Daily) Compared to AG-1749 (15 mg Once-Daily) in a 24-week Maintenance Treatment in Patients With Healed Erosive Esophagitis (EE).</official_title>
