  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to confirm the efficacy of TAK-438, once daily (QD), compared to
      lansoprazole for the maintenance treatment of healed erosive esophagitis and to determine the
      clinical dose.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
